Glyphosate, brand name RoundUp, is a very effective broad leaf herbicide.
Unfortunately, the side effects have proved to be very deleterious to the
environment. It is the main reason we are losing polinators, bees and
butterflies. The direct effects on humans of glyphosate, combined with gm
grains, have been hidden and are still denied by agribusiness.

Yes we have made a devil's bargain: we can feed a lot of people, but we
have paid a huge price with gm grains, herbicides and pesticides. And
perhaps most insidious, there is no way to back out of this without
starving millions of people in the process. I am not optimistic.

So, tend your gardens, and support your neighbors in tending theirs. This
is the best we can offer each other at this point.

Love you all!
Mom
